com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.dynamictype
Interface DynamicTypeRoot

public interface DynamicTypeRoot

A representation of the model object 'Dynamic Type Root'.

The following features are supported:

  • Mixed
  • XMLNS Prefix Map
  • XSI Schema Location
  • Dynamic Palette Entry
  • Dynamic Palette Stack
  • Dynamic Types

See Also:
